<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"> <channel> <title>Save with Sanders</title> <description>This site is a simple web application to calculate how much tax a person pays under Bernie Sanders&#39; tax plan </description> <link>http://savewithsanders.com/</link> <atom:link href="http://savewithsanders.com/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/> <pubDate>Mon, 11 Jan 2016 18:22:48 -0500</pubDate> <lastBuildDate>Mon, 11 Jan 2016 18:22:48 -0500</lastBuildDate> <generator>Jekyll v3.0.1</generator> <item> <title>Minimal Standalone Calculator</title> <description>&lt;script&gt; /** Get Input Value returns the value of an element by its ID. */ function getValue( id ){ return document.getElementById(id).value; } /** Calculate Tax A returns the result of plugging the current input values into the current plan. instead of parameters, these functions use getValue to read their inputs. */ function CalculateTaxA() { var finalValue = 0; return finalValue; } /** Calculate Tax B returns the result of plugging the current input values into Bernie&#39;s tax plan. */ function CalculateTaxB() { var finalValue = 0; return finalValue; } /** Set Results sets ResultA and ResultB to the results of their respective functions. */ function setResults() { document.getElementById(&#39;resultA&#39;).innerHTML = &#39; $&#39;+CalculateTaxA(); document.getElementById(&#39;resultB&#39;).innerHTML = &#39; $&#39;+CalculateTaxB(); } &lt;/script&gt; &lt;style&gt; /** * App Styles */ #app { font: 1em/1.4 Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: lightblue; line-height: 1.4; max-width: 650px; margin: auto; padding-left: 1%; } #app form &gt; div { padding: 0.5em 0; } #app legend { font-size: 1.1em; font-weight: 500; } #app label, #app input { width: 48%; display: inline-block; } &lt;/style&gt; &lt;div id=&quot;app&quot;&gt; &lt;form&gt; &lt;div&gt; &lt;legend&gt;Personal Income&lt;/legend&gt; &lt;div&gt;&lt;label for=&quot;income&quot;&gt;Income&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input id=&quot;income&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div&gt; &lt;legend&gt;Speculative Income&lt;/legend&gt; &lt;div&gt;&lt;label for=&quot;income-from-capital-gains&quot;&gt;Income from Capital Gains&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input id=&quot;income-from-capital-gains&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div&gt;&lt;label for=&quot;income-from-stocks&quot;&gt;Income from Stocks&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input id=&quot;income-from-stocks&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div&gt;&lt;label for=&quot;income-from-derivatives&quot;&gt;Income from Derivatives&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input id=&quot;income-from-derivatives&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div&gt;&lt;label for=&quot;income-from-bonds&quot;&gt;Income from Bonds&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input id=&quot;income-from-bonds&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div&gt; &lt;legend&gt;Estate Income&lt;/legend&gt; &lt;div&gt;&lt;label for=&quot;inheritance-size&quot;&gt;Inheritance Size&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input id=&quot;inheritance-size&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div&gt;&lt;label for=&quot;net-wealth&quot;&gt;Net Wealth&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input id=&quot;net-wealth&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div&gt; &lt;legend&gt;Student Loans&lt;/legend&gt; &lt;div&gt;&lt;label for=&quot;amount-in-student-loans&quot;&gt;Amount in Student Loans&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input id=&quot;amount-in-student-loans&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div&gt;&lt;label for=&quot;student-loan-rate&quot;&gt;Student Loan Rate&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input id=&quot;student-loan-rate&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div&gt;&lt;label for=&quot;months-left-until-repaid&quot;&gt;Months left until repaid&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input id=&quot;months-left-until-repaid&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div&gt; &lt;legend&gt;Family Expenses&lt;/legend&gt; &lt;div&gt;&lt;label for=&quot;number-of-dependents&quot;&gt;Number of Dependents&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input id=&quot;number-of-dependents&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div&gt;&lt;label for=&quot;monthly-health-insurance-payments&quot;&gt;Monthly Health Insurance Payments&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input id=&quot;monthly-health-insurance-payments&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/form&gt; &lt;p class=&quot;result&quot;&gt;Your tax is now&lt;span id=&quot;resultA&quot;&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class=&quot;result&quot;&gt;Your tax would be&lt;span id=&quot;resultB&quot;&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;button onclick=&quot;setResults()&quot;&gt;Calculate&lt;/button&gt; &lt;/div&gt; </description> <pubDate>Sun, 10 Jan 2016 00:00:00 -0500</pubDate> <link>http://savewithsanders.com/calc/</link> <guid isPermaLink="true">http://savewithsanders.com/calc/</guid> </item> </channel> </rss>